from dataclasses import dataclass, field
from typing import Any, Dict

@dataclass
class PREP:
    optimizer: Any
    schedulers: Dict = field(default_factory=dict)

# Initializing the PREP class
prep_instance = PREP(optimizer='adam', schedulers={'lr_scheduler': 'ReduceLROnPlateau'})

# Accessing the attributes of the initialized PREP class
print(prep_instance.optimizer)
print(prep_instance.schedulers)
